<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Scents by Rayo</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;}
body{background:#0b0b0b;color:white;}

/* NAV */
nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
padding:20px 50px;
position:fixed;
width:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
z-index:100;
}

.logo{
font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
color:#D4AF37;
font-size:24px;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
height:100vh;
background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592945403244-b3fbafd7f539') center/cover no-repeat;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
text-align:center;
position:relative;
}

.hero::after{
content:'';
position:absolute;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}

.hero-content{
position:relative;
z-index:2;
max-width:700px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:55px;
font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
}

.hero p{
color:#ddd;
margin-top:10px;
}

/* SECTION GENERAL */
section{padding:80px 40px;text-align:center;}

h2{
color:#D4AF37;
font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

p{color:#ccc;max-width:700px;margin:auto;line-height:1.7;}

/* GRID */
.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
background:#1a1a1a;
border-radius:15px;
overflow:hidden;
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{transform:scale(1.05);}

.card img{
width:100%;
height:260px;
object-fit:cover;
}

.price{color:#D4AF37;margin:10px 0;}

/* INSTAGRAM */
.insta-grid img{
height:160px;
border-radius:10px;
}

/* BUTTONS */
.btn{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:20px;
padding:12px 20px;
border-radius:5px;
text-decoration:none;
color:white;
}

.whatsapp-btn{background:#25D366;}
.insta-btn{background:#E1306C;}

/* FLOAT */
.whatsapp{
position:fixed;
bottom:20px;
right:20px;
background:#25D366;
padding:15px;
border-radius:50%;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
<div class="logo">SCENTS BY RAYO</div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
<div class="hero-content">
<h1>✨ A Scent of Renewed Joy</h1>
<p>
Scents by Rayo captures the essence of renewal and timeless joy.
Each fragrance is crafted to awaken your soul and elevate your presence.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section>
<h2>About</h2>
<p>
Scents by Rayo is more than fragrance — it is identity, elegance, and emotion.
Each scent is a symphony crafted to inspire confidence and leave a lasting impression.
More than a scent, it is your presence.
</p>
</section>

<!-- SHOWCASE -->
<section>
<h2>Signature Scents</h2>

<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615634262417-2bfa6c1a7f10">
<h3>Midnight Oud</h3>
<p class="price">₦45,000</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594035910387-fea47794261f">
<h3>Velvet Rose</h3>
<p class="price">₦38,000</p>
</div>
</div>

</section>

<!-- PROMISE -->
<section>
<h2>Our Promise</h2>
<p>
Long-lasting scents. Premium quality. Unforgettable presence.
Every bottle is crafted to elevate your confidence and leave a lasting memory.
</p>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section>
<h2>Testimonials</h2>
<p>"I’ve never felt this confident before wearing a fragrance."</p>
<p>"Luxury in a bottle. People notice immediately."</p>
</section>

<!-- INSTAGRAM -->
<section>
<h2>Instagram</h2>

<div class="grid insta-grid">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594035910387-fea47794261f">
</div>

<a href="https://instagram.com/YOURUSERNAME" class="btn insta-btn">View Instagram</a>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section>
<h2>Get Your Signature Scent</h2>
<a href="https://wa.me/2349060865009" class="btn whatsapp-btn">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
</section>

<a href="https://wa.me/2349060865009" class="whatsapp">💬</a>

</body>
</html>